Dyker Beach Park: Viewed northwestward from Cropsey Ave., at Fourteenth Ave., showing an artificial lake under construction. This is a set of three views. In the background of views one and two is seen the steeple of the Polytechnic Preparatory High School.

June 9, 1932.

P. L. Sperr.
